  "text": "However, the method used by Zhu in [CITATION_1] is not valid for n = 2. Recently, Chen and Hao in [CITATION_2] generalized the result by Zhu in [CITATION_3] to the critical Besov spaces. The aim of the present paper is to establish the global solutions of (1.1) with a class of highly oscillating initial velocity.",
